{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other one worked in Tischlerei.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It means in some building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He made for me a pipe from cherry wood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a pipe, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I worked outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the buildings commander would build some kind of factory in a firm called [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's German-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it's, it's a military-- some kind of military enterprise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then came-- the kapo was changed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a Russian-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a Russian soldier and very bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He hit me with a two by four.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And here I broke my some-- me vertebra-- whatever is the word there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later, I was-- I-- but little by little, you know-- I-- when I came for the first time into the concentration camp, of [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the first day, I looked over the window, where I saw one single picture, a wagon full of dead quote, unquote 'people' who were people, and 10, 10 [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It means 10 inmates dragging the wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one kapo in back with a whip, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They did everything to dehumanize myself, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was no end to beating, no matter of anything, no matter what-- the, the very first two weeks, with my taking cart to this, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then, the very same [NON-ENGLISH] came up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said to him when I was working in the field, we-- quasi-inspection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he said to me, Meilzynski, the transport list-- the first page from your transport list got lost.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They cannot reconstruct it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And three weeks or so later, the whole transfer from Bialystock who came was gassed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I and a lawyer, Duszinski from Poland, survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
